    <!--

    Useful documentation:
    * http://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-site-plugin/examples/sitedescriptor.html
    * http://andriusvelykis.github.io/reflow-maven-skin/

    Variable:
    * site-root - Root folder of the website (to be supplied using -Dsite.root=...)
    * project-version - Version of the project (defined in the POM file)
    * site-path - Local path of the website (to be supplied using -Dsite-path=file:///...)

    Links to external folders:
    /files -> http://knowledgestore.fbk.eu/files
    /ontologies -> http://knowledgestore.fbk.eu/ontologies
    /ks-server-http/webdocs -> http://knowledgestore.fbk.eu/ks-server-http/webdocs
    (for webdocs: the Enunciate plugin is not compatible with Java 1.8)

    -->

    <skin>
